      "id": "PopularPost39469",
      "post_content": "Great life gain for blue. Sure it often will be temporary, but then again if you do need it to survive chances are you aren't facing a control deck but more likely some agro and they may not have a way to remove this.\n  \n   \nBut when this really shines is when used with [Sanguine Bond](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sanguine Bond ) .",
      "posted_by": "Silverware",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost39469\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">Great life gain for blue. Sure it often will be temporary, but then again if you do need it to survive chances are you aren't facing a control deck but more likely some agro and they may not have a way to remove this. \r<br/> <br/>But when this really shines is when used with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Sanguine Bond \" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sanguine Bond \">Sanguine Bond </a>.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '39469'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy2871\">Silverware</span>\r\n                                (12/5/2009 7:34:29 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../I