    {
      "id": "PopularPost300083",
      "post_content": "The thing that made [Illusions of Grandeur](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Illusions of Grandeur) broken in the eyes of many was how deadly the cumulative upkeep made it when [Donate](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Donate)d. Here, the lifegain it halved and its usefulness for this application is also dampened. However, it's still worth noting that 10 life is nothing to scoff at, especially when running Phyrexian mana for things like [Immolating Souleater](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Immolating Souleater). It also gets you well along your way for [Test of Endurance](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Test of Endurance).",
      "posted_by": "Equinox523",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost300083\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">The thing that made <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Illusions of Grandeur\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Illusions of Grandeur\">Illusions of Grandeur</a> broken in the eyes of many was how deadly the cumulative upkeep made it when <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Donate\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Donate\">Donate</a>d.  Here, the lifegain it halved and its usefulness for this application is also dampened.  However, it's still worth noting that 10 life is nothing to scoff at, especially when running Phyrexian mana for things like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Immolating Souleater\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Immolating Souleater\">Immolating Souleater</a>.  It also gets you well along your way for <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Test of Endurance\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Test of Endurance\">Test of Endurance</a>.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '300083'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy1136\">Equinox523</span>\r\n                                (2/15/2013 10:23:05 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"